#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid ""
"Intro Implis L14: This chapter used the following operations:\n"
"§0, §1, §2, §3 (reversal of §4), §5, §6, §7 (changes §8 to §9),\n"
"§10 (changes §11 to §12 and §13), §14 (rewrite goal with §15), §16 (rewrite\n"
"assumption §17 using §18) and §19 (introduce cases §20 and §21)"
msgstr ""
"**Head of Operations**: You've really helped me out! Here's the last "
"problem. I inherited this from my predecessor. He claimed that if we could "
"solve this, everything would be back on track. But it always seemed far too "
"difficult for me to even try. Would you like to give it a go?\n"
"\n"
"**You**: Sure, let's have a look at it! Scribble, could you perhaps show me "
"another nice summary of what I've learned in the last five minutes? \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Here it is: \n"
"\n"
"## Notation\n"
"\n"
"| | Description |\n"
"|:--- |:---------------------------- | \n"
"| §0 | Implication | \n"
"| §1 | exactly-when / equivalence | \n"
"\n"
"## Tactics \n"
"\n"
"| Tactic | Example | \n"
"|:---------------- "
"|:----------------------------------------------------------------- | \n"
"| §2 | moves the left side of an implication in the goal into the "
"assumptions |\n"
"| §3 | reversal of §4 | \n"
"| §5 | applies implication “backwards” to the goal | \n"
"| §6 | applies implication “forwards” to an assumption | \n"
"| §7 | changes §8 to §9 |\n"
"| §10 | changes §11 to §12 and §13 | \n"
"| §14 | rewrites goal using equivalence §15 | \n"
"| §16 | rewrites assumption §17 using equivalence §18 | \n"
"| §19 | case distinction between §20 and §21 |"

