#: Game.Levels.Implis.L06_Iff
msgid "Intro Implis L06"
msgstr ""
"**Head of Operations**: We used to have a few conveyor belts that could run "
"in both directions. I had them all shut down as a precaution because the "
"latest manuals advise against using such double belts. But perhaps it's safe "
"to use them under certain conditions? What do you think about this scenario?"

