"With §0, you can generalize a proof goal\n"
"in the hope that a higher level of abstraction will allow for a simpler "
"proof.\n"
"More precisely, §1 replaces all occurrences of §2 in the proof goal with §3\n"
"(and adds the assumption §4).\n"
"\n"
"## Example\n"
