"degree of abstraction will allow for a simpler proof. More precisely, §1 "
"replaces all occurrences of §2 in the proof target with §3 (and adds the "
"assumption §4).\n"
"\n"
"## Example A goal of the form §5 can be converted to §7 using §6 (and then "
"simply proven using §8)."

