#: Game.Levels.Samarkand
#, fuzzy
msgid "Intro Samarkand"
msgstr ""
"A very colourful planet appears in the distance. As you get closer, you see "
"that large parts of its surface are decorated with elaborate geometric "
"patterns. But there are also a few undecorated areas, completely white. You "
"land in one of these white spots. **You**: Hello, is anyone there? The "
"planet's surface resembles a perfect sphere. You can see the horizon in all "
"directions. There is no one to be seen. You are about to turn back when you "
"discover something. **You**: Scribble, look over there, the planet has a "
"bump! It turns out that the \"bump\" is a small turtle lying on a coloured "
"background near the edge of the pattern. You carefully step onto the "
"patterned surface. The paint seems to be dry. **Arapuka**: Hello, you two, "
"come closer! It's nice to have visitors for once. **You**: What are you "
"doing here all alone?\n"
"\n"
"**Arapuka**: I'm working on a big work of art. I'll lie here until my shell "
"has taken on the pattern of the ground. Then I'll walk over to the spot "
"where this piece of pattern is still missing and lie down there until I've "
"transferred the pattern to the white surface of the planet. It takes a "
"while, so I could use some company. **You**: Great."

