#: Game.Levels.Ciao.L01
#, fuzzy
msgid "Conclusion Cia L01"
msgstr ""
"**You**: That wasn't so difficult... I wonder who sent it? And why? "
"**Scribble**: It was definitely a message from Ritha... Scribble gazes into "
"the distance. **Scribble**: I think she wanted to encourage us to keep "
"flying.\n"
"\n"
"**You**: But where to? **Scribble**: Oh, look, another message: *Dear "
"Earthlings,* *it was a pleasure to meet you! We are truly sorry that you "
"have strayed into our Formaloversum and cannot find your way home. But we "
"have some good news: you are not the only ones! Just fly quickly on to the "
"planet Zulip. There you will find many other Earthlings who have strayed "
"into the Formaloversum. Zulip is large, so you are sure to find a new home "
"there. Here are the coordinates:*\n"
"\n"
"[248-4804-180 | 844-1001-553](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/"
"channel/113489-new-members/)\n"
"\n"
"*With our sincerest regards* *– Your Formalosophers* **Scribble**: Well then "
"– let's go! [Don't be surprised: when you follow the coordinates, the "
"spaceship will accelerate to faster-than-light speed and you will "
"temporarily lose contact with the server. But that's okay. You will arrive "
"safely on Zulip.]"

