#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L10_DrinkersParadox
#, fuzzy
msgid "Intro Quantus L10"
msgstr ""
"**You**: Can you only ever talk in unison or all at once? There is another "
"long silence. Then suddenly: **Everyone**: There is one person among us who, "
"when they speak, everyone else speaks! You scratch your head. **Scribble**: "
"That's obvious. It's the same on every inhabited planet!\n"
"\n"
"**You**: What? **Scribble**: It's a version of Drinker's Paradox! Don't you "
"know it? Then you'd better look it up in your library! *In every bar, there "
"is one person who has the characteristic that everyone drinks when they "
"drink.* More precisely: in every bar that is not empty.\n"
"\n"
"**You**: I don't believe it. **Scribble**: I do. I even think you can prove "
"it. Here, try this!"

