msgid "Intro Euklid: shows encrypted message §0"
msgstr ""
"**Scribble**: This planet looks like a labyrinth. **You**: Or like a maze. "
"You slowly fly closer. **Scribble**: That's a library! We should definitely "
"take a closer look. But I don't know where to land. **You**: Maybe there?  "
"It looks like a small reading room. Can you do it? Scribble can do it. You "
"get out and look around. The shelves are metres high and densely packed with "
"thick-bound books. You pull one out at random, open a page and read the "
"following: §0 **You**:  Scribble, do you have any idea what this is? "
"**Scribble**: I think Gibberish is the technical term. So no, I have no "
"idea. You look at a few other books, but they all contain similar gibberish. "
