#: Game.Levels.Vieta
#, fuzzy
msgid "Intro Vieta"
msgstr ""
"Hello, is anyone there? You have landed in a heath landscape. There is no "
"one to be seen far and wide. Suddenly, an arrow whizzes right over your "
"head. **You**: Take cover!\n"
"\n"
"You throw yourself flat on the ground. You're about to crawl back to the "
"spaceship when a man emerges from behind a withered tree and waves friendly. "
"So you crawl towards him. **Vieta**: Don't be shy, ladies and gentlemen! My "
"name is Vieta. Welcome! Get up, the coast is clear.\n"
"\n"
"You rise cautiously, but another arrow whizzes past you. **You**: How do you "
"manage to live here? **Vieta**: Well, I've learned to always be in the right "
"place at the right time. Don't worry."

#: Game.Levels.Logo.L04_Assumption
