#: Game.Levels.Logo
#, fuzzy
msgid "Intro Logo"
msgstr ""
"Due to an unforeseen and non-canonical singularity in space-time, you have "
"accidentally stumbled into a parallel universe. As it appears, there is no "
"turning back. You had better prepare yourself to stay here and find your way "
"around. As it appears, there are many nice little planets here. All "
"habitable, and with up to seven sunsets a day included.\n"
"However, they are all inhabited by formalosophers, strange beings with "
"unusual mathematical obsessions. Unfortunately, word has spread that you "
"were a mathematician in your previous universe. You will find no peace here "
"until you learn to satisfy their insatiable thirst for knowledge.\n"
"\n"
"There are only two difficulties: firstly, the formalosophers appear to have "
"no deeper understanding of mathematics whatsoever, and secondly, they "
"communicate about mathematics exclusively in a dialect that is foreign to "
"you, which they call Leansch [liːnʃ].\n"
"\n"
"Fortunately, Scribble changed universes with you. Scribble is your little "
"SmartElf. Scribble may not be the mathematical genius you would have wished "
"for in this situation, but it seems he has learned Leansch somewhere. And "
"that is worth its weight in gold."

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L08_Rw
