"As you disembark, a formalosoph comes running towards you. He waves his arms "
"wildly. **Doorman**: No, no, you're expected down there. He lowers his "
"arms.\n"
"\n"
"**Doorman**: Well, never mind. Good afternoon, first of all! I'm just the "
"caretaker here. You are expected by a large delegation, but over there, in "
"the office building, of course. This is just our sleeping tower. Come on, "
"I'll take you over there. It won't take long.\n"
"\n"
"He leads you down one floor and asks you to get into \"transport capsules\", "
"one each. **Doorman**: We'll just slide over there in these capsules. Don't "
"worry, the track is clear! Unfortunately, we do have collisions here from "
"time to time, but at the moment the coast is clear. Everyone else is already "
"over there!"

